creator: HubEngage, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Use HubEngage™ to get the latest news and updates from your organization and to keep in touch with your colleagues and associates.

With HubEngage App you can:
- Keep track of latest news, events and other content relevant for you.
- Comment, like and share to become a brand advocate
- Take quizzes to learn more about your organization and policies
- Submit your own stories and give feedback
- Earn rewards for your actions, get on leaderboards and track your points.
- Instant Message your colleagues and associates

For more information go to http://www.hubEngage.com
